org.gridgain.jsr305
Annotation Type WillClose

@Documented
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=PARAMETER)
public @interface WillClose

The presence of this annotation on a method parameter indicates that the callee method will close this resource. The caller method doesn't have to close it itself. See JSR-305 for more information.
